\c 32
\s Ukuhlaliswa kwabakoRubeni labakoGadi labanye abakoManase
\p
\v 1 Mayelana labantwana bakoRubeni labantwana bakoGadi, babelenkomo ezinengi, ezinengi kakhulu. Sebebone ilizwe leJazeri\x + 32.3,35. 21.32.\x* lelizwe leGileyadi, khangela-ke, indawo yayiyindawo yenkomo.
\v 2 Ngakho abantwana bakoGadi labantwana bakoRubeni beza bakhuluma kuMozisi lakuEleyazare umpristi lakuziphathamandla zenhlangano, besithi:
\v 3 IAtarothi leDiboni\x + 32.34. 21.30.\x* leJazeri leNimra leHeshiboni leEleyale leSebamu leNebo\x + 32.38. 33.47. Dute. 32.49. 1 Lan. 5.8. Isa. 15.2; 46.1. Jer. 48.1,22.\x* leBeyoni,
\v 4 ilizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* eyalitshayayo phambi kwenhlangano yakoIsrayeli, liyilizwe lezinkomo; futhi izinceku zenu zilezinkomo\x + 21.24,34,35. 32.33.\x*.
\v 5 Basebesithi: Nxa sithole umusa emehlweni akho, ilizwe leli kaliphiwe inceku zakho libe yimfuyo; ungasichaphisi iJordani.
\p
\v 6 UMozisi wasesithi ebantwaneni bakoGadi lebantwaneni bakoRubeni: Abafowenu bazakuya empini, lina-ke lihlale lapha yini?
\v 7 Njalo lizadaniselani inhliziyo yabantwana bakoIsrayeli ukuze bangachaphi ukuya elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* ebanike lona?
\v 8 Benza njalo oyihlo mhla ngibathuma besuka eKadeshi-Bhaneya ukubona ilizwe\x + 13.3,21-33. Dute. 1.22-28.\x*.
\v 9 Ekuhambeni kwabo ukuya esihotsheni seEshikoli, balibona ilizwe, badanisa inhliziyo yabantwana bakoIsrayeli ukuze bangangeni elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayibanike lona.
\v 10 Ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* lwaseluvutha\x + 14.11. Dute. 1.34.\x* ngalolusuku, yasifunga isithi:
\v 11 Isibili kakho kumadoda enyuka esuka eGibhithe\x + 14.23. Dute. 1.35.\x*, kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amabili langaphezulu\x + 14.29.\x* ozalibona ilizwe engalifungela uAbrahama, uIsaka loJakobe\x + Gen. 50.24.\x*, ngoba kabangilandelanga ngokupheleleyo;
\v 12 ngaphandle kukaKalebi indodana kaJefune umKenizi\x + Josh. 14.6. 15.17.\x*, loJoshuwa indodana kaNuni, ngoba balandele iN\nd kosi\nd* ngokupheleleyo\x + 14.24. Dute. 1.36. Josh. 14.8,9.\x*.
\v 13 Lolaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* lwamvuthela uIsrayeli, yasibazulisa enkangala iminyaka engamatshumi amane\x + 14.33,34,35.\x*, kwaze kwaphela isizukulwana sonke esasenze okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 26.64,65.\x*.
\v 14 Khangelani-ke, selivukile esikhundleni saboyihlo, inzalo yabantu abonayo, ukwandisa futhi intukuthelo yeN\nd kosi\nd* evuthela uIsrayeli.
\v 15 Uba liphenduka ekuyilandeleni\x + Dute. 30.17. Josh. 22.16,18. 2 Lan. 7.19. 15.2.\x*, izaphinda njalo ibatshiye enkangala; njalo lizabhubhisa bonke lababantu.
\p
\v 16 Basebesondela kuye bathi: Sizakwakha lapha izibaya zezifuyo zethu, lemizi yabantwanyana bethu;
\v 17 kodwa thina sizahloma\x + Josh. 4.12,13.\x* silungile phambi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 32.20. 31.3.\x*, size sibafikise endaweni yabo, labantwanyana bethu bazahlala emizini evikelekileyo, ngenxa yabahlali belizwe.
\v 18 Kasiyikubuyela emizini yethu, abantwana bakoIsrayeli baze badle, ngulowo lalowo ilifa lakhe\x + Josh. 22.4.\x*.
\v 19 Ngoba kasiyikudla ilifa kanye labo ngaphetsheya kweJordani langaphambili, ngoba ilifa lethu selehlele kithi nganeno kweJordani empumalanga\x + 32.33. Josh. 12.1. 13.8.\x*.
\p
\v 20 UMozisi wasesithi kubo: Nxa lisenza linto, nxa lizahamba lihlomele impi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Dute. 3.18. Josh. 1.13,14.\x*,
\v 21 beselichapha iJordani, wonke ohlomileyo kini, phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 32.27,29,30,32. 31.5. Dute. 3.18. Josh. 4.13.\x*, ize ixotshe izitha zayo phambi kwayo\x + 32.39; 33.52; Eks. 15.9.\x*,
\v 22 lelizwe lehliselwe phansi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, khona emva kwalokho lizabuya, lingabi lacala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni lakuIsrayeli; lalelilizwe lizakuba yilifa lenu phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 23 Kodwa nxa lingenzi njalo, khangelani lizabe lonile eN\nd kosi\nd*ni; ngakho yazini ukuthi isono senu sizalithola\x + Gen. 44.16. Isa. 59.12.\x*.
\v 24 Zakheleni imizi yabantwanyana benu lezibaya zezimvu zenu\x + 32.16,34-38.\x*, njalo yenzani lokho okuphume emlonyeni wenu.
\v 25 Abantwana bakoGadi labantwana bakoRubeni basebekhuluma kuMozisi besithi: Izinceku zakho zizakwenza njengalokho inkosi yami ilaya.
\v 26 Abantwanyana bethu, omkethu, izimvu zethu, lazo zonke izifuyo zethu kuzakuba lapho emizini yeGileyadi;
\v 27 kodwa inceku zakho zizachapha, ngulowo lalowo ehlomele impi\x + 31.5.\x*, phambi kukaJehova empini, njengokutsho kwenkosi yami.
\v 28 UMozisi waselayezela ngabo kuEleyazare umpristi, loJoshuwa indodana kaNuni\x + 27.18.\x*, lenhloko zaboyise zezizwe zabantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\v 29 UMozisi wasesithi kubo: Nxa abantwana bakoGadi labantwana bakoRubeni bechapha lani iJordani, wonke ehlomele impi, phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, lelizwe lisehliselwa phansi phambi kwenu, khona lizabanika ilizwe leGileyadi libe yimfuyo.
\v 30 Kodwa uba bengachaphi lani behlomile, bazakuba lemfuyo phakathi kwenu elizweni leKhanani.
\v 31 Abantwana bakoGadi labantwana bakoRubeni basebephendula besithi: Lokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* esikutshilo kunceku zakho - sizakwenza njalo.
\v 32 Thina sizachapha sihlomile phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* siye elizweni leKhanani, ukuze imfuyo yelifa lethu ibe ngeyethu nganeno kweJordani.
\v 33 Njalo uMozisi wabanika, kubantwana bakoGadi lakubantwana bakoRubeni lakungxenye yesizwe sakoManase, indodana kaJosefa\x + Dute. 3.12-17. 29.8. Josh. 12.6. 13.8. 22.4. Nani 32.39.\x*, umbuso kaSihoni inkosi yamaAmori, lombuso kaOgi inkosi yeBashani, ilizwe lemizi yalo emingceleni, imizi yelizwe inhlangothi zonke\x + 32.4.\x*.
\p
\v 34 Labantwana bakoGadi bakha iDiboni\x + 32.3. 21.30.\x* leAtarothi\x + 32.3. 21.30.\x* leAroweri\x + Dute. 2.36.\x*
\v 35 leAtirothi-Shofani leJazeri leJogibeha,
\v 36 leBeti-Nimra leBeti-Harani, imizi evikelweyo, lezibaya zezimvu\x + 32.17.\x*.
\v 37 Labantwana bakoRubeni bakha iHeshiboni\x + 32.3; 21.25; Dute. 2.24; 3.6. Josh. 13.10. Hlu. 11.26. Neh. 9.22. Ngoma 7.4. Isa. 15.4;16.8,9. Jer. 48.2,34,45.\x* leEleyale leKiriyathayimi\x + 32.3.\x*
\v 38 leNebo\x + 32.3.\x* leBhali-Meyoni\x + Isa. 15.4; 16.9; Jer. 48.34.\x* (sekuguqulwe amabizo) leSibima\x + Eks. 23.13. Josh. 23.7.\x*; basebebiza amabizo emizi abayakhayo nga\add manye\add* amabizo.
\v 39 Labantwana bakoMakiri indodana kaManase\x + Gen. 50.23.\x* baya eGileyadi, bayithumba, bawakhupha amaAmori emfuyweni yawo ayekuyo.
\v 40 UMozisi wasenika uMakiri indodana kaManase iGileyadi, wasehlala kiyo.
\v 41 LoJayiri indodana kaManase wayathumba imizana yayo\x + Dute. 3.14. 1 Lan. 2.21,22,23.\x*, wayibiza ngokuthi yiHavothi-Jayiri\x + Josh. 13.30; Hlu. 10.4. 1 Kho. 4.13.\x*.
\v 42 LoNoba wayathumba iKenathi, lemizana yayo, wayibiza ngokuthi yiNoba ngebizo lakhe\x + 21.25.\x*.